column2:
"Hm, you really don't fall short, do you.
Your level of completion is completely
different."

"It was as if you said,
"I am partisan user <%me>. Face me!"
You should be very proud."

"The day will likely come that your name
is revealed as one who has reached his
pinnacle."

"That's a blessing more than I deserve
as an instructor.
Please work even harder!"

"うむ、やはり君は期待を裏切らないな。
完成度が一味も二味も違う。"

"パルチザン使い<%me>
ここにあり！　といったところだな。
大いに誇りを持っていい。"

"頂点を極めた者として、君の名を
披露する日が来るかもしれない。"

"教導官冥利に尽きるというものだ。
ますます精進したまえ！"
